Package org.cripac.isee.vpe.common

This package contains common concept classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ServerID
    Identifier of external servers.
    SparkStreamingApp
    The SparkStreamingApp class wraps a whole Spark Streaming application, including driver code and executor code.
    Stream
    A Stream is a flow of DStreams.
    Stream.Info
    The Info class is designed to force the output data INPUT_TYPE to be assigned to a stream, so that INPUT_TYPE matching checking can be conducted.
    Topic
    The Topic class is a wrapper for Kafka topics with additional information.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataType
    Enumeration of data types that can be accepted by applications.
